WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )


00:01:02.200 --> 00:01:02.759
The Artifact.

00:01:04.640 --> 00:01:06.040
Fine, you win.

00:01:06.359 --> 00:01:07.439
Are you going to kill me?

00:01:07.760 --> 00:01:08.599
Not necessarily.

00:01:09.079 --> 00:01:10.079
Depends on my mood.

00:01:10.359 --> 00:01:12.000
So how's your mood right now?

00:01:12.239 --> 00:01:13.640
Not great.

00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:15.680
What if I sang you a song?

00:01:16.079 --> 00:01:16.680
What song?

00:01:17.040 --> 00:01:17.680
The Daoist Scriptures.

00:01:18.879 --> 00:01:19.799
Don't like it.

00:01:20.200 --> 00:01:21.120
Gives me a headache.

00:01:21.280 --> 00:01:21.959
Alright then.

00:01:21.959 --> 00:01:23.799
Guess I'll just wait to die.

00:01:25.159 --> 00:01:26.400
Stop, stop, stop!

00:01:26.480 --> 00:01:27.959
Don't kill him! Don't kill him!

00:01:31.680 --> 00:01:32.280
Kill him.

00:01:33.359 --> 00:01:34.439
He must die.

00:01:35.680 --> 00:01:36.640
No, no, no, you can't kill him.

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:38.400
Murder is against the law.

00:01:39.280 --> 00:01:39.920
No such thing.

00:01:40.680 --> 00:01:42.359
When Shanhai City people commit crimes,

00:01:42.640 --> 00:01:44.599
they must be sentenced in Shanhai City.

00:01:44.840 --> 00:01:45.920
Hurry up and stab him to death.

00:01:45.920 --> 00:01:46.359
Quickly!

00:01:46.560 --> 00:01:47.280
One clean strike.

00:01:47.879 --> 00:01:49.680
Five percent compatibility.

00:01:50.120 --> 00:01:52.719
This Immortal Seed should beat the Rat's.

00:01:53.040 --> 00:01:54.079
It's a real boost.

00:01:54.400 --> 00:01:55.200
Five million.

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:56.599
Five million for his life.

00:01:57.400 --> 00:01:58.040
Fatty Geng,

00:01:58.719 --> 00:02:00.959
do you even hear yourself talking?

00:02:01.439 --> 00:02:02.239
Five million?

00:02:02.239 --> 00:02:03.719
Think you're tossing change to a beggar?

00:02:04.120 --> 00:02:04.719
If he dies,

00:02:05.239 --> 00:02:07.480
Qiushui City would be four against five.

00:02:07.959 --> 00:02:10.240
Easy to get crushed by smaller cities.

00:02:10.919 --> 00:02:11.439
So,

00:02:11.759 --> 00:02:12.960
what gets beaten down

00:02:13.159 --> 00:02:15.280
will be Qiushui City's reputation.

00:02:15.400 --> 00:02:16.479
Is Qiushui City's reputation

00:02:16.960 --> 00:02:18.280
really only worth five million?

00:02:27.479 --> 00:02:28.759
We're old classmates, right?

00:02:29.039 --> 00:02:29.840
We're all brothers.

00:02:29.840 --> 00:02:30.560
Give me a discount.

00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:33.840
Get your butt back where you just were.

00:02:34.120 --> 00:02:34.800
Go!

00:02:36.039 --> 00:02:38.080
Now you're all buddy-buddy with me?

00:02:39.000 --> 00:02:40.080
Why don't you talk about

00:02:40.080 --> 00:02:41.560
how back in school,

00:02:41.560 --> 00:02:43.080
you used to mess with me?

00:02:44.800 --> 00:02:47.240
One time I asked you for some coffee.

00:02:47.840 --> 00:02:49.280
You spent hundreds

00:02:49.280 --> 00:02:51.280
to send me an express delivery.

00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:53.520
And when it finally arrived,

00:02:54.039 --> 00:02:55.599
it was just a free sample packet.

00:02:55.879 --> 00:02:57.240
Cash on delivery, no less.

00:02:57.719 --> 00:02:58.960
Wasn't that rotten of you?

00:03:00.960 --> 00:03:01.680
And another thing,

00:03:02.080 --> 00:03:03.919
I just can't believe

00:03:04.199 --> 00:03:06.680
your dad would randomly chat with mine

00:03:06.840 --> 00:03:08.960
about that BS "raise a son tough" theory.

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:11.159
You dare say

00:03:11.439 --> 00:03:13.159
you weren't the one stirring things up?

00:03:15.919 --> 00:03:16.639
Fatty Geng,

00:03:17.159 --> 00:03:18.599
I'm telling you straight up,

00:03:18.800 --> 00:03:20.280
you're in my hands now.

00:03:20.439 --> 00:03:22.719
If I don't skin you alive,

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:24.520
I'll take your last name.

00:03:24.599 --> 00:03:25.319
You hear me?

00:03:27.240 --> 00:03:27.879
Don't laugh.

00:03:28.439 --> 00:03:29.360
I've got to take this call.

00:03:34.199 --> 00:03:35.360
Father, what is it?

00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:37.000
Your secretary already told me

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:38.240
about your situation there.

00:03:38.759 --> 00:03:40.280
I immediately

00:03:40.360 --> 00:03:42.599
called old Geng in Qiushui City.

00:03:42.719 --> 00:03:43.680
I already got the payoff.

00:03:45.840 --> 00:03:47.159
So in other words,

00:03:48.159 --> 00:03:50.280
I won't get anything now, is that it?

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:53.680
Put Su Yang on the phone.

00:04:02.280 --> 00:04:03.599
Do me a favor,

00:04:03.879 --> 00:04:05.199
and let him go.

00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:07.639
The favor you owed me before,

00:04:07.960 --> 00:04:09.319
we'll call it even.

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:10.599
How about it?

00:04:11.759 --> 00:04:13.039
A life for a life.

00:04:14.719 --> 00:04:15.360
That's fair.

00:04:15.360 --> 00:04:16.399
Ask for more, Su Yang.

00:04:16.480 --> 00:04:17.319
Ask for more.

00:04:17.319 --> 00:04:18.399
Su Yang, more...

00:04:20.959 --> 00:04:21.879
Actually, I think...

00:04:29.040 --> 00:04:29.759
Um...

00:04:31.240 --> 00:04:33.439
That five million you just mentioned,

00:04:33.519 --> 00:04:34.279
I agree to it.

00:04:34.759 --> 00:04:35.480
And then?

00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:36.079
I also want

00:04:36.519 --> 00:04:38.079
some expensive coffee.

00:04:38.319 --> 00:04:39.560
The most expensive, finest kind.

00:04:39.959 --> 00:04:41.079
No cash on delivery this time.

00:04:43.079 --> 00:04:44.120
This outfit looks great.

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:34.839
Don't waste my time.

00:05:35.120 --> 00:05:35.720
Take the picture.

00:05:38.439 --> 00:05:39.160
Line up.

00:05:40.519 --> 00:05:41.319
Take the picture.

00:05:44.360 --> 00:05:45.920
Okay, shoot now, shoot now.

00:06:04.519 --> 00:06:05.120
Shoot.

00:06:05.800 --> 00:06:06.720
Line up!

00:06:11.879 --> 00:06:13.000
Shoot, shoot.

00:06:13.160 --> 00:06:14.160
Shoot now, shoot now.

00:06:46.360 --> 00:06:47.160
Just as I thought,

00:06:47.519 --> 00:06:49.439
I can only train hard where Tongtong is.

00:06:49.680 --> 00:06:51.439
Senior Brother never gives me this chance.

00:06:54.639 --> 00:06:55.319
Senior Brother.

00:06:55.879 --> 00:06:57.399
Tongtong seems a bit unwell.

00:06:57.600 --> 00:06:58.319
I know.

00:06:59.360 --> 00:07:01.519
Shouldn't we head back to rest then?

00:07:05.639 --> 00:07:07.360
We can play several more times.

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:08.079
So,

00:07:08.800 --> 00:07:11.120
you think we should, when she's happiest,

00:07:11.519 --> 00:07:13.079
lock her back in that cold room,

00:07:13.519 --> 00:07:15.600
and on that cold bed tell her,

00:07:15.759 --> 00:07:16.600
"You're a patient,

00:07:16.879 --> 00:07:17.839
you need to rest,

00:07:18.680 --> 00:07:19.279
you're...

00:07:19.560 --> 00:07:20.360
dying soon."

00:07:21.399 --> 00:07:22.199
Is that what we should do?

00:07:25.800 --> 00:07:26.600
Patients, you see,

00:07:27.720 --> 00:07:30.000
don't like being treated like patients.

00:07:31.519 --> 00:07:32.319
Sometimes,

00:07:33.240 --> 00:07:35.160
they just want to be like normal people.

00:07:37.480 --> 00:07:38.439
Missed it again, huh?

00:07:40.199 --> 00:07:42.000
Just want to be like everyone else.

00:07:45.800 --> 00:07:46.560
Let's catch this one, okay?

00:07:46.560 --> 00:07:47.160
Okay.

00:07:47.160 --> 00:07:47.920
Alright, come on.

00:07:49.519 --> 00:07:50.920
Senior Brother's trying to tell me,

00:07:51.920 --> 00:07:53.639
even after stepping on the immortal path,

00:07:54.079 --> 00:07:55.319
you can't become arrogant.

00:07:56.079 --> 00:07:58.079
Keeping a level head is what matters most.

00:07:59.000 --> 00:08:00.720
Always remember your roots,

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:02.000
remember who you are.

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:02.800
Slow down, slow down.

00:08:02.800 --> 00:08:04.040
Just like the teacher said,

00:08:04.040 --> 00:08:05.079
stay humble and patient.

00:08:06.040 --> 00:08:07.040
I'm gonna make Senior Brother

00:08:07.240 --> 00:08:08.879
sink into the depths of my wealth,

00:08:09.680 --> 00:08:11.959
let him indulge in all worldly luxuries,

00:08:12.480 --> 00:08:14.240
until he's too hooked to leave.

00:08:14.600 --> 00:08:15.279
That way,

00:08:15.920 --> 00:08:18.040
I'll become the top disciple of our sect.

00:08:27.680 --> 00:08:28.319
Hey!

00:08:28.439 --> 00:08:29.319
Where's my horse?

00:08:30.199 --> 00:08:31.000
Pulling a cart.

00:08:31.120 --> 00:08:32.639
You took my horse to pull a cart?

00:08:33.039 --> 00:08:34.320
Right now, immediately,

00:08:34.320 --> 00:08:35.279
take my horse

00:08:35.399 --> 00:08:36.480
and get your ass back home!

00:08:36.799 --> 00:08:37.480
Dad,

00:08:37.960 --> 00:08:39.000
do you even understand cultivation?

00:08:39.840 --> 00:08:40.639
What the hell?

00:08:41.600 --> 00:08:42.360
You don't understand cultivation.

00:08:42.360 --> 00:08:43.240
Got it, got it!

00:08:46.840 --> 00:08:48.240
Spending directly on Senior Brother

00:08:48.240 --> 00:08:49.840
would eventually make him suspicious.

00:08:50.200 --> 00:08:50.720
So cute.

00:08:50.720 --> 00:08:53.000
Going through Tongtong feels more natural.

00:08:53.840 --> 00:08:55.440
Plus, Senior Brother loves Tongtong,

00:08:55.879 --> 00:08:57.519
so this plays right to his heart.

00:08:58.639 --> 00:08:59.320
Sure enough,

00:08:59.679 --> 00:09:02.039
sometimes cunning works wonders.

00:09:02.039 --> 00:09:03.399
Su Yang, you're amazing!

00:09:04.919 --> 00:09:05.519
Let's go.

00:09:05.519 --> 00:09:06.200
Come on.

00:09:35.639 --> 00:09:36.320
Tongtong.

00:09:37.080 --> 00:09:37.759
Tongtong.

00:10:23.480 --> 00:10:24.159
Does it still hurt?

00:10:32.639 --> 00:10:33.600
Not anymore.

00:10:35.080 --> 00:10:35.720
Okay.

00:10:36.279 --> 00:10:37.080
I understand.

00:10:37.559 --> 00:10:38.440
Rest a little longer.

00:10:38.840 --> 00:10:39.600
Okay.

00:10:40.639 --> 00:10:41.440
Go to sleep.

00:11:12.960 --> 00:11:13.799
Su Yang.

00:11:14.559 --> 00:11:16.039
Senior Brother, what's wrong?

00:11:16.320 --> 00:11:17.000
Move aside.

00:11:17.679 --> 00:11:18.639
Or die.

00:11:20.320 --> 00:11:20.919
Move.

00:11:20.919 --> 00:11:21.879
He really might kill you all.

00:11:21.879 --> 00:11:22.399
Move aside!

00:11:27.639 --> 00:11:29.200
Move! I said move aside!

00:11:29.879 --> 00:11:30.559
I've moved.

00:11:31.039 --> 00:11:31.679
What is it?

00:11:31.879 --> 00:11:33.120
That Artifact you mentioned,

00:11:33.759 --> 00:11:35.120
I brought one back.

00:11:35.799 --> 00:11:36.639
I gave it to Tongtong.

00:11:37.879 --> 00:11:39.159
No effect.

00:11:40.279 --> 00:11:41.519
No effect at all.

00:11:42.240 --> 00:11:43.080
Impossible.

00:11:46.840 --> 00:11:47.440
How about this,

00:11:47.799 --> 00:11:49.080
give me five minutes.

00:11:49.080 --> 00:11:50.000
Let me look into it.

00:11:50.000 --> 00:11:51.360
If I can't figure it out,

00:11:51.399 --> 00:11:52.759
then you won't have to kill me.

00:11:52.759 --> 00:11:54.000
I'll jump down myself, okay?

00:11:54.679 --> 00:11:55.360
Five minutes.

00:12:02.480 --> 00:12:03.240
Phone, my phone!

00:12:03.240 --> 00:12:04.840
Give me the phone, hand it over!

00:12:14.879 --> 00:12:15.480
Hey.

00:12:15.759 --> 00:12:16.639
At today's registration venue,

00:12:16.639 --> 00:12:17.639
what exactly happened?

00:12:17.840 --> 00:12:19.200
Tell me in the shortest way possible.

00:12:26.240 --> 00:12:27.200
The little Taoist...

00:12:27.480 --> 00:12:28.279
From Qiushui City...

00:12:38.600 --> 00:12:39.720
Hey, what is it?

00:12:39.840 --> 00:12:40.679
Your Fat Bro is busy here.

00:12:40.679 --> 00:12:41.440
Fatty Geng,

00:12:41.480 --> 00:12:43.240
if you hang up on me right now,

00:12:43.240 --> 00:12:44.919
I won't let you off, even as a ghost.

00:12:46.960 --> 00:12:49.240
So you've run into trouble?

00:12:50.039 --> 00:12:51.159
Normally speaking,

00:12:51.159 --> 00:12:52.639
I really should hang up on you.

00:12:52.639 --> 00:12:53.639
Fatty Geng, you...

00:12:53.759 --> 00:12:54.720
No, no.

00:12:54.879 --> 00:12:55.480
Look,

00:12:56.120 --> 00:12:56.759
Daddy Geng.

00:12:56.960 --> 00:12:58.000
Daddy, okay?

00:12:58.000 --> 00:12:58.919
I'll call you Daddy, all right?

00:12:58.919 --> 00:12:59.879
I was wrong.

00:12:59.879 --> 00:13:01.679
Just tell me about the Taoist's Artifact.

00:13:01.679 --> 00:13:03.120
What's the deal with it?

00:13:03.679 --> 00:13:04.799
Say it a couple more times.

00:13:04.799 --> 00:13:05.480
Say it twice more.

00:13:05.480 --> 00:13:07.399
Daddy! I don't have time to joke around.

00:13:07.399 --> 00:13:09.399
If you keep stalling, I'm going to die!

00:13:10.679 --> 00:13:11.399
I see.

00:13:11.600 --> 00:13:12.360
Fine, then.

00:13:12.919 --> 00:13:14.360
You owe me one for this.

00:13:14.440 --> 00:13:15.720
And transfer me another 1,000 yuan.

00:13:15.879 --> 00:13:17.440
After all, compared to being Young Lord,

00:13:17.559 --> 00:13:19.639
I prefer my identity as a businessman.

00:13:19.720 --> 00:13:21.399
No problem. Just hurry.

00:13:21.639 --> 00:13:23.480
I hate doing business with stingy people.

00:13:23.519 --> 00:13:24.279
Speak.

00:13:24.279 --> 00:13:26.200
Here's roughly what happened.

00:13:26.679 --> 00:13:28.919
On Mount Wenhe in our Qiushui City,

00:13:28.919 --> 00:13:30.120
there's an ancient Taoist temple.

00:13:30.480 --> 00:13:31.679
The Immortal Realm bestowed a blessing,

00:13:31.679 --> 00:13:33.879
and an ancient bronze lamp inside

00:13:33.879 --> 00:13:34.879
suddenly showed strange signs,

00:13:35.240 --> 00:13:36.519
choosing who to bless.

00:13:36.919 --> 00:13:39.159
But everyone inside the temple

00:13:39.159 --> 00:13:41.000
were all followers of Master Randeng,

00:13:41.159 --> 00:13:42.320
sharing the same origin.

00:13:42.360 --> 00:13:44.279
So all of them received the blessing,

00:13:44.480 --> 00:13:46.200
so the Intent inside this Artifact

00:13:46.200 --> 00:13:47.480
to be completely used up.

00:13:47.960 --> 00:13:49.360
So now that Artifact

00:13:49.840 --> 00:13:51.480
is basically no different from junk.

00:13:52.120 --> 00:13:54.120
Otherwise, why do you think Su Yang

00:13:54.120 --> 00:13:56.000
could take it away so easily?

00:13:57.559 --> 00:13:58.320
Remember to transfer the money.

00:13:58.320 --> 00:13:59.120
Not WeChat. I got it.

00:13:59.120 --> 00:14:00.080
Withdrawals have fees.

00:14:01.440 --> 00:14:02.559
I know the reason now.

00:14:02.960 --> 00:14:04.879
The situation back then was like this:

00:14:05.080 --> 00:14:07.480
The Intent in that Artifact was so strong,

00:14:07.480 --> 00:14:08.639
which caused everyone in the temple

00:14:08.639 --> 00:14:10.559
to be blessed by the Artifact's master.

00:14:10.720 --> 00:14:12.120
And precisely because of this,

00:14:12.120 --> 00:14:14.120
all Intent in the Artifact was drained.

00:14:14.120 --> 00:14:15.159
So when used on Tongtong,

00:14:15.159 --> 00:14:16.240
it had absolutely no effect.

00:14:16.240 --> 00:14:18.159
For that little Taoist, it was simpler.

00:14:18.159 --> 00:14:19.159
He devoured all the...

00:14:19.159 --> 00:14:21.039
blessed ones in the temple's... uh...

00:14:21.080 --> 00:14:21.879
Dharma forms.

00:14:22.519 --> 00:14:23.679
Because they shared the same origin,

00:14:23.679 --> 00:14:25.960
the compatibility grew extremely fast.

00:14:25.960 --> 00:14:27.240
That's basically the situation.

00:14:27.360 --> 00:14:28.679
If you don't believe my explanation,

00:14:28.679 --> 00:14:29.559
just kill me.

00:14:46.000 --> 00:14:47.200
I was, I was, I was...

00:14:47.200 --> 00:14:48.399
just saying it casually.

00:14:56.399 --> 00:14:57.360
Here's a gift for you.

00:14:57.519 --> 00:14:58.440
Just joking with you.

00:14:58.440 --> 00:14:59.440
Don't be so tense.

00:15:01.279 --> 00:15:02.200
I just thought, you know,

00:15:02.240 --> 00:15:04.159
the security in this hotel isn't great,

00:15:04.320 --> 00:15:05.240
so I tested it for you.

00:15:05.279 --> 00:15:06.440
Look at that door.

00:15:06.559 --> 00:15:07.279
Look, look, look.

00:15:07.840 --> 00:15:08.639
This door,

00:15:09.000 --> 00:15:10.440
how flimsy it is!

00:15:15.600 --> 00:15:16.480
You know,

00:15:16.480 --> 00:15:17.879
I'm just a lunatic.

00:15:17.960 --> 00:15:19.279
I have my episodes now and then,

00:15:19.279 --> 00:15:20.320
go a little crazy sometimes.

00:15:21.240 --> 00:15:22.200
Don't take it seriously.

00:15:25.519 --> 00:15:26.799
You wouldn't really

00:15:27.120 --> 00:15:28.720
hold a grudge against a lunatic, would you?

00:15:29.000 --> 00:15:30.039
I even gave you a gift.

00:15:46.879 --> 00:15:48.440
Look, what a nice door.

00:15:49.000 --> 00:15:49.879
It looks so sturdy.

00:15:49.879 --> 00:15:50.919
Where's my door?

00:15:51.120 --> 00:15:52.240
Who tore down my door?

00:15:52.240 --> 00:15:53.720
I've got something to handle. I'm off.

00:16:01.080 --> 00:16:02.360
The prize for the contest,

00:16:02.559 --> 00:16:04.039
it's not a used Artifact, is it?

00:16:04.879 --> 00:16:05.639
Absolutely not.

00:16:05.960 --> 00:16:06.919
Alright then, bye.

00:16:11.240 --> 00:16:12.600
I'm sure you're all already

00:16:12.600 --> 00:16:13.600
looking forward to our contest.

00:16:13.600 --> 00:16:15.159
The contestants are waiting backstage.